Interface ListIterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<java.lang.Object>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MyListImpl.ListIteratorImpl

    public interface ListIterator
extends java.util.Iterator<java.lang.Object>
    This interface is a kind of a template for the list iterators. Provides implementing classes with a set of methods extended from java.util.Iterator interface. Also contains methods for iterating backwards and replacing elements.
    Version:
    1.0, 13 Nov 2017
    Author:
    Hrynevych Pavlo
